    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. Delivering 414 hp to the rear wheels via a 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission (DCT), this chassis features a functional M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise handling. Preventative maintenance is up to date, with both rod bearings and throttle actuators recently addressed to ensure long-term reliability. The suspension bushings remain firm, and the hydraulic steering rack offers excellent feedback. While the exterior shows minor signs of spirited road use, the drivetrain and subframe are in robust condition, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
